                <head>Pointed</head>
                <origin>N. Y. Courier and Enquirer</origin>
                <commentary>"Reason and common sense seem to be asserting their supremacy . . . ."</commentary>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Republican paper claims that they and Lincoln are in favor of supporting
                    the Constitution and restoring fugitives to justice.</summary>
